{"tid":160572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保良局訓練營的成魔之路","createTime":"2017-03-17T20:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T13:22:37.000Z","uid":66324,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a759a1fefef40af0683f615ead2fc7174b9db49c","tid":160572,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T20:07:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://medium.com/@drasticmeasures/%E4%BF%9D%E8%89%AF%E5%B1%80%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E7%87%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%88%90%E9%AD%94%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF-4c7e7e9bc6cb#.e25rtd1pp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40drasticmeasures%2F%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%2589%25AF%25E5%25B1%2580%25E8%25A8%2593%25E7%25B7%25B4%25E7%2587%259F%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%25AD%2594%25E4%25B9%258B%25E8%25B7%25AF-4c7e7e9bc6cb%23.e25rtd1pp&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86Zk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=1a90013d\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@drasticmeasures/%E4%BF%9D%E8%89%AF%E5%B1%80%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E7%87%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%88%90%E9%AD%94%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF-4c7e7e9bc6cb#.e25rtd1pp</a><br />\n<br />\n昨日傳媒報道，黃大仙重案組調查訓練營涉嫌虐待兒童。蘋果動新聞主持還說是否虐兒不到你我判斷，因為警方已經介入了。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但現實是，大家不應抱有任何期望，因為這些訓練營是獲得香港政府支持，要知道吳克儉也是保良局訓練營結業會操的嘉賓。</strong></span>盧錦昌接受蘋果訪問時聲稱「我哋亦都唔驚嘅」，並指讓警方調查是公道做法。這是不是涉嫌虐兒，疑犯會不會被繩之於法，大家心裡有數。"},{"pid":"e9355202ad9016c452ab38ae1a8e8999ab185365","tid":160572,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T20:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cafa965d4be02f3c03d8be8b466a7084ed4739f2","tid":160572,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T20:13:51.000Z","msg":"我相信未必入到佢地<br />\n 但我相信公義 人渣終會得到制裁"},{"pid":"dc7241602469b525412d72c68d99e297d5bfc6f9","tid":160572,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T20:15:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我相信未必入到佢地<br />\n 但我相信公義 人渣終會得到制裁</blockquote><br />\n唔好講入唔入到, 你覺得會落charge? <img src=\"/ass